I think the generator and sequence name should be different to minimize confusion because the generator represents a Hibernate object and the sequence represents a Postgres object. Adding a suffix should suffice.
Example:
@GeneratedValue(generator = "alert.audit_entries_id_seq_generator", ...)
@SequenceGenerator(name = "alert.audit_entries_id_seq_generator", sequenceName = "alert.audit_entries_id_seq", ...)

